title: Tahm Kench Skins
body: I was wondering if there would be any upcoming Tahm Kench skins as his Master Chef Tahm Kench Skin at the moment does not seem very appealing to me and I would love to see a new Tahm Kench skin coming out soon.

replies.body: given how popular he is for being a pain in the ass, he might recieve one soon, depends on what the rito gods want.
